<p>
The toolbar is a small pane in the bottom-right of the MinoCloud.com site and any <a href="/docs/Apps">app</a> powered by MinoCloud. It helps you to navigate between MinoCloud <a href="/docs/Apps">apps</a> such as the <a href="/docs/Browser">browser</a> and other <a href="/docs/Apps">apps</a> that you have activated.
</p>

<p>
The toolbar also provides access to the visual notifications you have received and shows a red notice when you have unread notifications.
</p>